window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>When my best friend and I fell for the same guy in middle school, I stepped back.</p> <p>I'd always expected to dance at their wedding.</p> <p>Not sit in the back pew of her funeral.</p> <p>I left town for my own reasons, but now that I'm back, it’s clear Sebastian Montgomery isn't the same man I left.</p> <p>He's hard. Broken.</p> <p>And a single father to an adorable little girl.</p> <p>When it turns out he’s my new neighbor, I can’t stay away.</p> <p>But I know I’m playing with fire and the heat between us burns enough to scorch.</p> <p>I thought I was over my crush.</p> <p>But now it might crush me.</p>"; 
